column5: I had heard the Wal mart in Bradford had some,but when we arrived today,the last one just got sold.  Any help would be thankful.   Or if anyone has one for sale or for loan,please pm me.  Thanks again.
Man.... and you've only been Married for THREE days........
LOL  If I had one Wayne,I would of been up this morning.Pouring at 3:45 when I woke up,so I stayed compfy. Clearing tonight.I,ll see ya tomorrow.  Was he out there again today?
I didn't get out to the hangar that early this morning. Was one on the end of the runway last night around 6pm as well...think it was a hen though.
